==Whẹdida Etọn==
Onuamadike to pipehẹ owhẹ sọha di kande-wiawe (52) he gando mẹhuhu, ajojijẹ, mẹfinfin, awhanfunnú he ma sọgbe hẹ osẹ́n bibẹpli podo owhẹ devo lẹpo. Na taun tọn, e yin whẹsadokọna to whenuena e fin Uche Okereafor to lẹdo Festac tọn to ayimatẹn awọ̀nlin tọn mẹ to azan konukundopotọ Abọhusun owhe 2017, bọ sọ biọ akuẹ yi livi awe dollar tọn.
